{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "vop", "internal": "block_begin_if", "icon": "VOP/block_begin_if", "since": "14.5", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Block Begin If"], "extent": [92, 111]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Marks the start of an if code block."], "extent": [111, 156]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The Block Begin If node begins a conditional block of code.  If the\nfirst input evaluates to true, the corresponding End block\u2019s outputs\nwill correspond to the End block\u2019s inputs.  If it evaluates to false,\nhowever, the inputs of the End block will be ignored, and instead\nthe corresponding inputs of the Begin block will pass directly to\nthe outputs of the End block."], "extent": [156, 526]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [526, 532], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The block nodes are usually implicitly put down with the higher\n    level For Loop, For-Each Loop, While Loop tools."], "extent": [532, 655]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [655, 667], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Paired Block"], "extent": [667, 685], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["A path to the paired block forming a begin/end block pair.\n        Both nodes must be in the same network.  Nodes wired between\n        the pair are enclosed in a convex hull and are placed inside\n        a code block.  Depending on the types of the begin and end\n        blocks, different control flow can be done on the block."], "extent": [685, 1023]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Number of Outputs"], "extent": [1023, 1046], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["By default an output is generated for each input.  This allows\n        the specification of extra outputs.  If no input wire is present,\n        the value is assumed to be ", {"type": "code", "text": ["0"]}, " and the type must be specified."], "extent": [1046, 1263]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The outputs of an End block are paired with the outputs of the\n        Begin block.  If no names are present, the pairing is done in\n        order.  If names are present, they are paired by name."], "extent": [1263, 1468]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1468, 1477], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_begin", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_begin"}], "extent": [1477, 1506]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_begin_if", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_begin_if"}], "extent": [1506, 1538]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_begin_for", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_begin_for"}], "extent": [1538, 1571]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_begin_foreach", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_begin_foreach"}], "extent": [1571, 1608]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_end", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_end"}], "extent": [1608, 1635]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_end_while", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_end_while"}], "extent": [1635, 1668]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/block_end_breakif", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/block_end_breakif"}], "extent": [1668, 1703]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Block Begin If"], "summary": ["Marks the start of an if code block."]}